		Building SerialICE-1B
		Building SerialICE-1B

The steps required to build SerialICE are shown below.

  »  Set your environment.
  »  Build the run-time library using the following command.

	nmake

  »  Make a set of SerialICE Kernel ROMS
for your Target board using the following commands.

	cd bsps
	nmake kcputype

Where cputype is one of the following 4101, 4011, 4102.

Then use the kernel file bsp/kcputype.rec  to make a set of ROMs for
your Target board.

